   Contacting NIDA

   If you have a question for our staff, please send e-mail to
   Information@lists.nida.nih.gov
   or call 301-443-1124

   Questions of a technical nature relating to the web site can be
   addressed to webmaster@lists.nida.nih.gov

   (Local Date & Time: Wednesday, January 30, 2002 : 12:56:38 PM)
